A file-based project management and bug-tracking tool.

Version: 0.2-DEV


Installation

pip install git+https://github.com/dudarev/progress.git#egg=progress


Usage

usage: p [COMMAND [ARGS]]

    typing just 'p' will output all items to do
    
    add    [-i [(step,task,issue)]] -t TITLE
    clean  clean progress.yaml, move done items to progress.yaml.history
    count  count items done and to be done
    done   [n] - mark item n done
    help   print help
    html   generate progress.html
    log    [-i item_type] [-d] - log items
    

Inspirations:

"A journey of a thousand miles begins with a single step." 
-- Confucius 

